			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65032085" name="comment_link_65032085" href="//hardware.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23558333&amp;cid=65032085" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65032085)" >Re:</a>


