	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65032139">I even have old tech magazines from the 1960ies, with nuclear batteries dating back to the end-1950ies. And how, I pray, are Pioneer 11, Voyager 1 and Voyager 2 powered, so far out in Space without enough sunlight for solar cells? Right! With a nuclear battery.
